Detects APT41 dual-use behavior, including mixed credential abuse, cloud-style access patterns, and cross-environment movement.


index=auth OR index=endpoint OR index=cloud OR index=proxy
(
    EventCode=4624 OR EventCode=4625
    OR Image="*powershell*"
    OR Image="*wmic*"
)
| stats count dc(host) as hosts dc(src_ip) as ips values(Image) as tools by user
| eval hybrid=if(hosts>4 AND ips>2 AND count>10,1,0)
| where hybrid=1
| sort - hosts
